!imported node-docker-sample is your project name

// if you do some changes to docker file first need to build it
docker build -t node-docker-sample .

// create docker container
docker run -p 3000:3000 node-docker-sample

==============================================

// if you stop the docker contaninrer use this for re run it

# List all containers (including stopped ones)
docker ps -a  

#
docker start -a <container_id_or_name>





